        "title": "Ojalgo: Defining whether a matrix is stable in Java",
        "body": "<p>I'm trying to solve M (NxN) linear systems (Ax = B, B = [b1,b2,...bM]) using Ojalgo. Thanks to <strong>apete<\/strong>'s counsel, I successfully managed to check if A (A, B are objects of type PrimitiveMatrix) is singular but it seems that sometimes it's also unstable..\nIt would be really useful for me to determine if this matrix is stable or not.<\/p>\n\n<p>Any help would be most appreciated. Thank you!<\/p>\n",
